description: Returns the list of powers that can be specified for your Amazon Lightsail container services. The power specifies the amount of memory, the number of vCPUs, and the base price of the container service.

nested_items.name: powers
nested_items.description: An array of objects that describe the powers that can be specified for a container service.

nested_items.name: powerId
nested_items.description: The ID of the power ( nano-1).

nested_items.name: price
nested_items.description: The monthly price of the power in USD.

nested_items.name: cpuCount
nested_items.description: The number of vCPUs included in the power.

nested_items.name: ramSizeInGb
nested_items.description: The amount of RAM (in GB) of the power.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The friendly name of the power ( nano).

nested_items.name: isActive
nested_items.description: A Boolean value indicating whether the power is active and can be specified for container services.
